For the questions:<br>
<br>
1.  How or in what do you combine items?<br>
a: An elemental grimoire.  <br>
<br>
2. Where do you get it from?<br>
a: Someone in your mage guild sells them.  I personally bought mine from the guy in the back of the Qeynos herb shop. Runs about 15pp if I remember correct.<br>
